viewData.name: PhiBrows Drawing Pencil Set (2pcs)
viewData.short_description: Best quality eyebrow pencils for easy shape drawing. It differs from ordinary pencils due to its flat surface which, when using the edge, ensures that the new shape or outline of the eyebrow is drawn accurately. A simple surgical or office scalpel can be used for sharpening the pencil. Each set contains 2 pencils.
